<html><head><title>Another Hot Zone Weekend!</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Another Hot Zone Weekend!</h3><p>Starting today and ending on Monday, EverQuest 2 is hosting another 'Hot Zone Weekend', in which players will receive extra experience for fighting in certain zones. These zones include Loping Plains, Lesser Faydark, Steamfont Mountains, Butcherblock Mountains and Greater Faydark. Soak up that extra EXP today!</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Friday, 15 May, 2009<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=52440">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=52440</a><br>Printed On: Wed Sep 5 20:13:19 PDT 2012<br>©2008 IGN Entertainment</font></span>